HEADWORD: Glairy
<hw>Glair"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Like glair, or
partaking of its qualities; covered with glair; viscous and transparent;
slimy.</def> <rj><au>Wiseman.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
